of my own.

22:06.920 --> 22:08.640
Like Glastonbury?

22:08.640 --> 22:10.200
Less muddy, more magical.

22:10.200 --> 22:13.040
So, there's gonna be luxury yurts,
regular yurts, slam poetry,

22:13.040 --> 22:16.680
yoga, Ed Sheeran. I mean, everything
you've ever wanted, right?

22:16.680 --> 22:19.640
