22:19.640 --> 22:21.320
You sure you don't want some piff?

22:21.320 --> 22:22.800
All right, why not?

22:24.800 --> 22:26.960
Somewhere around here. Exactly. Hey!

22:26.960 --> 22:29.040
Put that out, will ya?

22:29.040 --> 22:31.880
Not getting extra hours
cos of your sort. Your sort?

22:31.880 --> 22:35.160
