than just doing a decent days' work.

22:38.880 --> 22:41.760
Oh, stealing, dealing drugs.
Why you saying that? Cos he's black?

22:41.760 --> 22:42.960
Because he's here.

22:42.960 --> 22:44.320
So are you, mate.

22:44.320 --> 22:47.200
Yeah, because of his sort.
Come here, give me the joint.

22:47.200 --> 22:48.360
What? What are you doing?

22:48.360 --> 22:50.720
Just give me the joint.
Stop it. Stop!

22:50.720 --> 22:54.160
That's enough! What are you doing?!

22:54.160 --> 22:57.920
All right, stop... Stop it!

22:59.520 --> 23:01.920
An eye for an eye makes
the whole world blind.

23:03.280 --> 23:06.760
Cut it out! Right now!

23:18.640 --> 23:20.160
Who's this belong to?

23:20.160 --> 23:21.720
It's his. No, it ain't.

23:21.720 --> 23:25.880
Somebody owns up
or everyone gets five more hours.

23:25.880 --> 23:29.040
You can't do that. He can do that.
Mr Wilder's a senior officer.

23:29.040 --> 23:30.120
Whose is it?

23:30.120 --> 23:32.520
I've just told you whose it is.
It's his.

23:32.520 --> 23:34.240
Ask her, she knows.

23:34.240 --> 23:36.640
If you know something, speak up.

23:47.120 --> 23:49.200
We... It's mine.

23:54.640 --> 23:56.560
No, it isn't. It's mine.

23:57.840 --> 23:59.840
Five more hours for both of you.

23:59.840 --> 24:01.480
