behind bars.

24:27.160 --> 24:28.520
Understood?

24:28.520 --> 24:30.520
Yes.

24:34.000 --> 24:36.760
All right, pack it up people.
We'll do it all again tomorrow.

24:36.760 --> 24:40.000
Apart from the fighting.
And the ganja.

24:42.680 --> 24:44.120
