in Miami right now.

26:43.320 --> 26:44.600
Come on, Es. Let's go.

26:47.320 --> 26:48.880
Shit, man.

26:48.880 --> 26:50.360
Home, now.

26:50.360 --> 26:51.600
You seem tense, blud.

26:51.600 --> 26:55.480
They do virtual porn - you should
have a tug, let off some steam.

26:59.240 --> 27:00.480
Come on, let's go home.

27:00.480 --> 27:02.720
Here, Es.

27:02.720 --> 27:05.000
Take this 50.
Buy yourself something nice.

27:05.000 --> 27:06.520
She don't want it.

27:06.520 --> 27:07.720
Yeah, I do. It's free money.

27:07.720 --> 27:09.680
No, it's not. Let's go.

27:12.360 --> 27:14.520
Es, I'll hold if for you, yeah?
Yeah!

27:15.520 --> 27:17.160
Why do I have to keep telling you
all the time?

27:17.160 --> 27:18.920
Stop hanging with these people.

27:18.920 --> 27:21.000
Come on. Why do I have to keep...

27:22.360 --> 27:23.840
And, uh, we're very proud

27:23.840 --> 27:26.520
of the fact that,
from those humble beginnings,

27:26.520 --> 27:31.880
we now find ourselves standing here
in this 50,000 square foot space.

27:33.480 --> 27:36.320
But let's, uh, let's,
let's talk more about, uh,

27:36.320 --> 27:39.440
the family side of the business
and, uh...

27:42.720 --> 27:46.400
..where we've come from
and really where we intend to go.

27:47.600 --> 27:50.360
You can really see
the...the year-on-year growth,

27:50.360 --> 27:53.320
and it's this growth
that will mark a significant return

27:53.320 --> 27:55.000
on your investment.

27:57.800 --> 28:01.200
And make a partnership
with Halloran and Son

28:01.200 --> 28:03.480
the only sensible choice.

28:05.560 --> 28:06.920
Xie xie.

28:06.920 --> 28:08.640
♪ Then we danced all night... ♪

28:08.640 --> 28:10.200
Zhao!

28:13.840 --> 28:16.160
I'm very sorry.
Please excuse my daughter.

28:18.280 --> 28:22.440
She loves all things British -
One Direction, Little Mix,

28:22.440 --> 28:23.720
Brooklyn Beckham...

28:23.720 --> 28:27.400
Well, um, on behalf of Britain,
I can only apologise.

28:29.560 --> 28:31.440
Yes.

28:37.880 --> 28:40.920
Our company has built
an impeccable reputation

28:40.920 --> 28:42.200
for integrity and honesty.

28:42.200 --> 28:44.240
